  "remarks": "Senior member of Al-Qaida (QDe.004). Reportedly killed in January 2020 in Yemen. Wanted by the Saudi Arabian Government for terrorism. Father's name is Abdullah Saleh al Zahrani. Physical description: eye colour: dark; hair colour: dark; complexion: olive. Speaks Arabic. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. Saudi Arabian passport number E126785, issued on 27 May 2002, expired on 3 Apr. 2007. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368\n(2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded\non 30 October 2023."
